>- 60gr đường bột</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 1 l&ograve;ng đỏ trứng</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 150gr bột m&igrave;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 50gr bột hạnh nh&acirc;n</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 15gr bột cacao&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">-&nbsp;15 bột d&acirc;u</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- Chocolate trắng</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- Kẹo m&agrave;u</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- Que kem</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n						</tbody>\r\n					</table>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" style="padding-left: 3px;" width="100%">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" width="100%">\r\n					<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">\r\n						<tbody>\r\n						</tbody>\r\n					</table>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" style="padding-left: 3px;" width="100%">\r\n					<div>\r\n						<span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Đến phần h&agrave;nh động n&agrave;y: &gt;:D&lt;</span></div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" width="100%">\r\n					<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">\r\n						<tbody>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/3/4/2120/110304mbtcookiekem12.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 1:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Để bơ mềm rồi đ&aacute;nh đều lần lượt với: đường, trứng, bột m&igrave;, bột hạnh nh&acirc;n n&agrave;y.</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/3/4/2120/110304mbtcookiekem22.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 2:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Tiếp theo, ta chia hỗn hợp bột l&agrave;m hai phần bằng nhau r&ugrave;i pha bột cacao v&agrave; bột d&acirc;u v&agrave;o từng phần nh&eacute;!</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/3/4/2120/110304mbtcookiekem32.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 3:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- C&aacute;n bột th&agrave;nh miếng d&agrave;y chừng 1cm. Sau đ&oacute;, bọc bột lại bằng nilon v&agrave; cho v&agrave;o ngăn&nbsp;m&aacute;t của&nbsp;tủ lạnh khoảng 30&#39;.</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/3/4/2120/110304mbtcookiekem42.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 4:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Lấy bột ra, cắt th&agrave;nh từng phần giống như chiếc kem rồi gắn que gỗ v&agrave;o v&agrave; đem nướng ở 180 độ C trong khoảng 15&#39; nghen.</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/3/4/2120/110304mbtcookiekem52.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 5:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Để trang tr&iacute;. C&aacute;c bạn đun chảy chocolate trắng ra rồi nh&uacute;ng một đầu que kem v&agrave;o.</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/3/4/2120/110304mbtcookiekem62.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<p align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Sau đ&oacute;, nhanh ta rắc kẹo m&agrave;u l&ecirc;n khi m&agrave; chocolate chưa bị kh&ocirc; lại nh&eacute;!</span></p>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n						</tbody>\r\n					</table>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" style="padding-left: 3px;" width="100%">\r\n					<div>\r\n						<span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;">Vậy l&agrave; những que kem thật xinh xắn kh&ocirc;ng bao giờ chảy đ&atilde; ra đời.... </span></div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" style="padding-left: 3px;" width="100%">\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						<img _fl="" align="middle" src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/03/04/110304MBTcookiekemsp1.jpg" style="margin: 5px;" width="500" /></div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-style: italic;">Chỉ cần chịu bỏ thời gian l&agrave; c&aacute;c bạn sẽ l&agrave;m được th&ocirc;i! </span></div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						<img _fl="" align="middle" src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/03/04/110304MBTcookiekemsp2.jpg" style="margin: 5px;" width="500" /></div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-style: italic;">G&oacute;i gh&eacute;m v&agrave;o v&agrave; mang đi tặng th&ocirc;i nhỉ? <span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '110304MBTcookiekemsp2.jpg', NULL, 1);
INSERT INTO `leadings` VALUES (9, 'Ốc quế kem giòn tan rôm rả ngày cuối tuần', 'Chính xác hơn thì đây là một loại bánh có tên là Florentines của nước Ý các bạn ạ!', '<p class="sapo">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class="content">\r\n	<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" style="padding-left: 3px;" width="100%">\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						<span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Chuẩn bị những nguy&ecirc;n liệu sau:</span></div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" width="100%">\r\n					<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">\r\n						<tbody>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/2/25/2236/110225mbtocquenguyenlieu2.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 110gr bột m&igrave;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 250gr bơ</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 150gr đường</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 40gr dừa kh&ocirc;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 100gr hạnh nh&acirc;n l&aacute;t (rang ch&iacute;n)</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 4ml vani</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- 50gr chocolate</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic; color: rgb(0, 0, 205); font-weight: bold;">- Kem tươi</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n						</tbody>\r\n					</table>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" style="padding-left: 3px;" width="100%">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" width="100%">\r\n					<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">\r\n						<tbody>\r\n						</tbody>\r\n					</table>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" style="padding-left: 3px;" width="100%">\r\n					<div>\r\n						<span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Đến phần h&agrave;nh động n&agrave;y: &gt;:D&lt;</span></div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" width="100%">\r\n					<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">\r\n						<tbody>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/2/25/2236/110225mbtocque12.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 1:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Trước ti&ecirc;n, ta cần đun chảy bơ ra n&agrave;y</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/2/25/2236/110225mbtocque22.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 2:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Tiếp theo l&agrave; cho tất cả c&aacute;c nguy&ecirc;n liệu c&ograve;n lại v&agrave;o trộn đều.</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/2/25/2236/110225mbtocque32.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 3:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Chia hỗn hợp bột th&agrave;nh từng phần nhỏ ra khay nướng c&oacute; l&oacute;t giấy nến (giấy chống d&iacute;nh) nh&eacute;!</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/2/25/2236/110225mbtocque42.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 4:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Rồi ấn mỏng ra n&agrave;y v&agrave; đem b&aacute;nh đi nướng ở 180 độ C trong khoảng 6&#39;.</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/2/25/2236/110225mbtocque52.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 5:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Khi vừa lấy b&aacute;nh ra khỏi l&ograve;, c&aacute;c bạn nhanh tay cuốn b&aacute;nh lại th&agrave;nh h&igrave;nh ốc quế nh&eacute;! Bước n&agrave;y&nbsp;cần cẩn thận&nbsp;ch&uacute;t x&iacute;u bởi b&aacute;nh vẫn c&ograve;n rất n&oacute;ng m&agrave;.</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/2/25/2236/110225mbtocque62.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 6:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Đun chảy chocolate ra n&agrave;o!</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n							<tr>\r\n								<td style="padding-left: 15px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 12px;" valign="top">\r\n									<table align="left" cellspacing="0">\r\n										<tbody>\r\n											<tr>\r\n												<td style="padding-right: 15px;" valign="top">\r\n													<div>\r\n														<img src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/2/25/2236/110225mbtocque72.jpg" style="border: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);" /></div>\r\n													<div>\r\n														&nbsp;</div>\r\n												</td>\r\n											</tr>\r\n										</tbody>\r\n									</table>\r\n									<div>\r\n										<span style="font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;">Bước 7:</span></div>\r\n									<div>\r\n										&nbsp;</div>\r\n									<div align="justify">\r\n										<span style="font-style: italic;">- Sau đ&oacute;, nh&uacute;ng 1 đầu của ốc quế v&agrave;o chocolate n&egrave; hoặc c&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể tr&aacute;ng chocolate v&agrave;o b&ecirc;n trong ốc quế cũng được r&ugrave;i bơm đầy kem v&ocirc; l&agrave; xong.</span></div>\r\n								</td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n						</tbody>\r\n					</table>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="left" style="padding-left: 3px;" width="100%">\r\n					<div>\r\n						<span style="font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold;">C&aacute;c bạn để kem lạnh một ch&uacute;t ăn cho ngon nh&aacute;! </span></div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div>\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td align="center" style="padding-left: 3px;" width="100%">\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						<img _fl="" align="middle" src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/02/25/110225MBTocquesp1.jpg" style="margin: 5px;" width="500" /></div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-style: italic;">Chiếc ốc quế n&agrave;y sẽ thơm hơn hẳn so với c&aacute;c loại th&ocirc;ng thường đấy! </span></div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						&nbsp;</div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						<img _fl="" align="middle" src="http://k14.vcmedia.vn/Images/Uploaded/Share/2011/02/25/110225MBTocquesp2.jpg" style="margin: 5px;" width="500" /></div>\r\n					<div align="center">\r\n						<span style="font-style: italic;">Nếu kh&ocirc;ng uốn th&agrave;nh h&igrave;nh ốc quế được th&igrave; m&igrave;nh c&oacute; thể ăn theo kiểu n&agrave;y nh&eacute;! <span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n				</td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '110225MBTocquesp2.jpg', NULL, 1);

